B.apa=new A.pO(B.QX,"dan\u0131\u015fmanl\u0131k","Dan\u0131\u015fmanl\u0131k","Birebir online veya y\xfcz y\xfcze ger\xe7ekle\u015ftirilen, miza\xe7 odakl\u0131 ki\u015fisel geli\u015fim ve kariyer y\xf6nelimi dan\u0131\u015fmanl\u0131\u011f\u0131.","D\xfczenli seanslarda miza\xe7 tipinizin sizi nas\u0131l \u015fekillendirdi\u011fini ke\u015ffeder, sa\u011fl\u0131kl\u0131 \xf6r\xfcnt\xfcler geli\u015ftirme yolculu\u011funa \xe7\u0131kars\u0131n\u0131z.")
